---
---
<section id="about" class="section about-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-left reveal-left">
        <div class="tag">About Us</div>
        <h2 class="about-title">Who We Are</h2>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <p class="about-text">
          VAC Global Solutions is a next-generation SaaS-driven consulting firm that bridges
          the gap between technology and business operations. We help SMEs and growing enterprises
          replace fragmented workflows with unified, scalable systems.
        </p>
        <p class="about-text">
          Unlike pure consultants or software vendors, we deliver both strategy and technology
          in one engagement — no middlemen, no hand-offs, no excuses.
        </p>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top:2rem;">
          Start Your Journey →
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="about-right">
        <div class="pillar reveal stagger-1">
          <div class="pillar-icon" style="background:rgba(0,45,98,0.08);color:var(--primary)">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M8 21h8M12 17v4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="pillar-title">Technology-First</h4>
            <p class="pillar-desc">We embed SaaS products like ERP directly into consulting engagements for real, lasting change.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="pillar reveal stagger-2">
          <div class="pillar-icon" style="background:rgba(0,45,98,0.08);color:var(--secondary)">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22C6.48 22 2 17.52 2 12S6.48 2 12 2s10 4.48 10 10-4.48 10-10 10z"/><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="pillar-title">Operations Focus</h4>
            <p class="pillar-desc">Streamlining supply chain, finance, HR and production for measurable efficiency gains.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="pillar reveal stagger-3">
          <div class="pillar-icon" style="background:rgba(59,130,246,0.08);color:var(--accent-blue)">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="2" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12"/><path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="pillar-title">Global Reach</h4>
            <p class="pillar-desc">Supporting SMEs across industries and geographies with enterprise-grade scalable systems.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.about-section { background: var(--neutral); }
.about-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 6rem;
  align-items: center;
}
.about-title {
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 3rem);
  font-weight: 800;
  color: var(--primary);
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  letter-spacing: -0.03em;
}
.divider {
  width: 48px;
  height: 4px;
  background: var(--primary);
  border-radius: 4px;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}
.about-text {
  color: var(--muted);
  line-height: 1.8;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  font-size: 1.05rem;
}

.pillar {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 1.25rem;
  padding: 1.5rem;
  background: var(--white);
  border-radius: 16px;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  transition: transform 0.3s var(--ease-out), box-shadow 0.3s;
}
.pillar:hover {
  transform: translateY(-4px);
  box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,45,98,0.1);
}
.pillar-icon {
  width: 52px; height: 52px;
  border-radius: 12px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.pillar-title {
  font-family: var(--font-head);
  font-size: 1rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--text);
  margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
}
.pillar-desc {
  font-size: 0.875rem;
  color: var(--muted);
  line-height: 1.6;
}

@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
}
</style>
